<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org5f74cb9">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Arithmetic statistics at the <a href="https://swc-math.github.io/aws/2014/index.html">2014 AWS</a>.
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>The <a href="https://swc-math.github.io/aws/2014/2014HoShankarProblems.pdf">problem set</a> is phenomenal.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>There are several arithmetic statistics videos on the <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/vantageseminar/history-of-vantage-talks?authuser=0">VANTAGE seminar</a> record.</li>
